data.description: **Seller is offering a price reduction and/or unique credits to help save you money, ACT NOW** Your future now has an address, welcome home. Located in the fast growing area of Boiling Springs, this beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bath crafstman style home is tucked away in a quaint neighborhood that allows for peaceful living quarters while being close to all of the cities amenities. This home boasts an open floor plan, well lit kitchen and living room with granite countertops and a stone crafted fire place. This home is perfect for entertaining with a spacious back patio and fenced in yard. The owners suite which includes a full bath and two additional rooms are all located on the main floor. Upstairs you will find your bonus room that is perfect for an extra sleeping area, media room, exercise room, office, or whatever you can think up that fits your needs. Dont miss your opportunity to visit this stunning residence today.
